"We start at our issued Invoice of 3000 euros for Smith & Co. Let's also "
"assume that other Invoices are open for different customers."
msgstr "Nous commençons par notre facture émise de 3000 euros pour Smith & Co. Supposons aussi que d'autres factures sont ouvertes pour différents clients."

#: ../../accounting/bank/reconciliation/use_cases.rst:74
msgid ""
"We receive our bank statement and not only the invoice of Smith & Co has "
